{"tid":814291,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【異動股】毛記曾跌穿招股價 高位累跌九成","createTime":"2018-09-11T06:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T05:18:22.000Z","uid":54870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"286f7187b6ebb2bec46edd6ddb9c0536300ed68c","tid":814291,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"今年3月底掛牌的毛記葵涌（1716），今早曾低見1.18元，跌5.6%，午後報1.21元跌逾2%。<br />\n毛記上市價為1.2元，上市首日曾高見11.76元，以今早低位計累跌九成。<br />\n<br />\n毛記早前公佈截至3月底止全年業績，集團期內收益錄8,674.7萬元，按年減8.9%，主要是印刷及其他媒體服務收入下跌，毛利率亦大減9.9個百分點，至51.32%，行政開支大幅上升2.3倍，至2,625.1萬元，主要受累期內錄得上市開支1,624.3萬元，拖低純利按年大縮80.9%，至691.7萬元，每股盈利3.4仙，不派息。<br />\n<br />\n以今日低位股價計，集團市盈率（PE）近50倍。"},{"pid":"1f882e41d8f5e4114634b340c53dd8d5b2af95fd","tid":814291,"uid":54870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"★毛記果然是保本首選！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/byMReS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/byMReS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★講穩陣，毛記無得輸！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bycGaS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bycGaS</a>"},{"pid":"0f98e6a1425ecd9cd6ad10f735c0d32b68959c0f","tid":814291,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966adf32d675f2e05fec647b2aa774abea38ce71","tid":814291,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"鞭老貓啱呀，清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bad74e2271087c1dc7bde35d66d87dd7179f325","tid":814291,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966adf32d675f2e05fec647b2aa774abea38ce71","tid":814291,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"鞭老貓啱呀，清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}